title: MNF recap and Mrs. Lynch
itunes:title: MNF recap and Mrs. Lynch
description:
A room filled with heroes - Dan Hanzus, Gregg Rosenthal, Chris Wesseling and Marc Sessler – recap the return of Monday Night Football including the Falcons taking down the Eagles and the 49ers defeating the Vikings. Then, the heroes preview the Thursday Night Football game between the Broncos and the Chiefs before Conor Orr joins the show to break down the latest NFL news.
